Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.54,0:00:03.30,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.78,0:00:04.55,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.70,0:00:09.40,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,要是推銷電話就掛了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.05,0:00:12.55,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,是新田的媽媽啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.18,0:00:15.45,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我和新田住在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.43,0:00:18.52,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,好疼
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.93,0:00:19.70,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.85,0:00:22.20,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,義史 剛才那個女孩子是怎麼回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.37,0:00:23.72,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,女孩子 什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.33,0:00:26.02,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你是不是聽到什麼幽靈在說話了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.99,0:00:27.34,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼可能啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.69,0:00:29.79,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼… 好可怕
Comment: 0,0:00:01.00,0:00:01.00,*Default,,0,0,0,,OP
