Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.63,0:00:35.10,hinamatsuri_opcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur6}我們究竟相距多遠呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.20,0:00:42.20,hinamatsuri_opcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur6}偶然一瞬 想起了你的容貌模樣
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.92,0:01:03.28,hinamatsuri_opcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur6}在記憶之中 你微笑著的側臉
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.60,0:01:09.01,hinamatsuri_opcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur6}平淡無奇的日常 是無可替的寶物
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.22,0:01:13.81,hinamatsuri_opcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur6}這份思念之情 現在終於意識到了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.97,0:01:16.62,hinamatsuri_opcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur6}和你歡笑度過的時光
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.62,0:01:19.43,hinamatsuri_opcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur6}和你爭論淚流的曾經
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.45,0:01:23.79,hinamatsuri_opcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur6}我們攜手的每一天 令人無比憐愛的每一天
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.07,0:01:26.56,hinamatsuri_opcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur6}十分珍惜
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.29,0:01:31.99,hinamatsuri_opcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur6}我們究竟相距多遠呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.34,0:01:38.24,hinamatsuri_opcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur6}我又回憶起你的溫暖
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.32,0:01:43.05,hinamatsuri_opcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur6}遙遙可見的那條街道的燈火
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.14,0:01:47.54,hinamatsuri_opcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur6}你正展露著笑容嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.00,0:00:01.00,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,——OP——
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.89,0:02:09.35,hinamatsuri_guochang,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fad(960,834)\pos(942,0)}第六話 新田的父親是個花花公子
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.26,0:02:06.11,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你在幹什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.22,0:02:07.21,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我在參拜啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.39,0:02:09.79,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,老爺子去世了 我來問候他一下
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.32,0:02:12.63,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,老爺子死了嗎 他不是還會動嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.02,0:02:15.07,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不是那個老爺子 是我老爸
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.50,0:02:17.25,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,接著你要跟我家裡人寒暄兩句
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.76,0:02:18.56,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,雛 拜託你了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.28,0:02:21.07,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,交給我吧 我行事很穩重的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.36,0:02:22.19,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,滿心不安
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.48,0:02:24.22,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,雛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.73,0:02:27.41,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,這是我媽 和我妹妹美佳
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.03,0:02:28.83,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,打個招呼吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.49,0:02:34.63,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我叫安達雛 我13歲了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.11,0:02:37.83,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸進了監獄 我無親無故
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.84,0:02:40.06,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,就跟新田一起生活了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.70,0:02:45.42,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,新田待人很親切 每天過得都很開心
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.32,0:02:47.69,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,是 是這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.26,0:02:51.27,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那個 你是什麼時候跟我哥住在一起的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.75,0:02:55.02,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,等等 給雛提的問題可以讓我回答嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.06,0:02:56.07,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你哪來的經紀人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.87,0:02:58.98,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你媽媽那邊也沒有什麼親人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.30,0:03:06.40,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我叫安達雛 我13歲了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.42,0:03:07.34,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你是發神經的機器人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.70,0:03:08.32,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,跟我過來一下
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.91,0:03:13.75,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,接下來就讓我來解釋 你先在外面玩會吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.84,0:03:15.65,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我可是按著我們排練好的說的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.77,0:03:17.19,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,但你臨場反應不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.88,0:03:20.68,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,為了不把事情變複雜 才把你當成是借住在我這的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.10,0:03:23.60,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,要是暴露了惹上麻煩 我們都沒什麼好果子吃的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.87,0:03:25.13,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我在努力啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.11,0:03:30.34,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你就努力地待在外邊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.55,0:03:33.08,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,她身上還發生過這麼多事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.74,0:03:35.54,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,是因為一次打鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.18,0:03:38.40,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,全家一起吃飯的時候她媽媽被槍擊了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.82,0:03:41.93,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,然後她父親應戰後 殺掉了兩個傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.79,0:03:46.01,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,他以前經常照顧我 真是感覺坐立不安
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.09,0:03:48.38,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我就收留了她
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.12,0:03:51.88,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,雛沒受傷嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.24,0:03:54.55,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,她當時在吃乾燒蝦仁吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.36,0:03:56.60,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,吃乾燒蝦仁
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.35,0:03:57.98,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,再來一份
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.36,0:04:02.87,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,估計是過於震驚 她就只記得當時的乾燒蝦仁了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.20,0:04:05.21,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼會有這種事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.04,0:04:09.38,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我剛收留她的時候 她幾乎說不出話
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.92,0:04:12.83,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,但最近 她終於能慢慢地
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.93,0:04:16.38,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,開始說話了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.90,0:04:22.30,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,但是她剛才不是說什麼每天都過得很開心嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.07,0:04:23.94,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.81,0:04:28.16,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,大概是她不想讓我擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.96,0:04:30.03,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,在勉強自己吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.15,0:04:32.24,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.10,0:04:35.87,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,所以說 過去的事情就別再問了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.07,0:04:39.84,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,乾燒蝦仁什麼鬼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.48,0:04:44.28,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我可真是不得了啊 估計有做演員的才能吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.38,0:04:48.13,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,義史 差不多該吃晚飯了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.80,0:04:49.69,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.78,0:04:55.71,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我們好想吃… 義史做的飯啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.55,0:04:57.57,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我是客人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.67,0:04:59.96,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我可是聽說哥你要回來
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.06,0:05:03.24,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,所以才放心地在大白天就開始喝酒了 你看
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.25,0:05:04.39,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你這也太奇怪了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.64,0:05:05.93,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我該從哪裡吐槽啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.95,0:05:09.98,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣啊 我懂了 我做就是囉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.63,0:05:12.65,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,燒個開水 也就三分鐘的事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.66,0:05:14.57,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不 我都用不了三分鐘
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.76,0:05:15.73,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,兩分鐘就足夠了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.01,0:05:16.97,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我懂
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.20,0:05:19.76,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道了 我去做
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.30,0:05:24.06,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,小雛都上初一了啊 在學校過得開心嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.32,0:05:25.85,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,一點也不開心 一直睡覺
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.92,0:05:27.69,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,但是吃午飯很開心
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.85,0:05:31.41,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,可惡 為了讓你去學校我可是花了不少錢啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.66,0:05:34.92,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那你作業應該也不做吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.87,0:05:36.74,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,作業…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.59,0:05:39.65,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我今天拿過來了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.95,0:05:42.56,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,她把作業拿過來了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.18,0:05:45.87,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,平時都沒見她做過 在這個時候拿出來…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.42,0:05:49.44,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不過等下 要是她開始做作業 話題也該結束了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.08,0:05:51.89,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,好 好作業 非常好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.06,0:05:54.02,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我看一下
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.71,0:05:57.22,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,名字要好好寫上去才行
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.36,0:05:58.03,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.25,0:06:03.13,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}新田雛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.21,0:06:03.98,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,新田雛？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.91,0:06:06.15,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,這個啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.04,0:06:09.15,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我跟學校那邊去商量的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.18,0:06:11.74,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,怕到時候因為姓不同 雛會被問東問西
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.75,0:06:13.91,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,考慮到這點才讓她跟我姓的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.73,0:06:18.66,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,她接受了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.74,0:06:19.59,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那是自然啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.95,0:06:20.62,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,是吧 雛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.03,0:06:29.45,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我叫安達雛 我13歲了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.89,0:06:38.29,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥做的飯就是好吃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.04,0:06:42.32,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,但這麼一看 你過得還真是挺開心的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.33,0:06:44.25,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,跟他在一塊 什麼最讓你開心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.69,0:06:46.87,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,倒是有很多啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.74,0:06:49.64,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,應該是去夜總會吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.81,0:06:55.19,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不是 那個… 她說她想去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.00,0:06:56.92,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不不不
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.18,0:07:00.75,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道 我幹了蠢事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.45,0:07:04.60,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 我想看到她的笑容
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.69,0:07:07.18,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,一不小心就寵過頭了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.71,0:07:11.38,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,以後要注意點哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.04,0:07:14.50,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,這個設定還真是厲害啊 你們也太好騙了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.23,0:07:16.34,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你也再喝點吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.60,0:07:17.68,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,也是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.97,0:07:24.98,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼會有煙花啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.74,0:07:29.52,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,夏天有親戚的孩子們來了 那時候剩下的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.84,0:07:30.94,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你在幹什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.11,0:07:37.40,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,在燒排隊的螞蟻
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.32,0:07:40.13,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,傻瓜
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.37,0:07:46.16,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不管是什麼生物 它們都在拚命地活著
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.84,0:07:49.08,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,大家都是朋友啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.71,0:07:54.39,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,這些傢伙 也是朋友嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.49,0:07:57.47,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.93,0:08:02.05,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,這是個弱肉強食的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.59,0:08:06.64,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,強者會隨性救人 也會隨性殺人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.78,0:08:10.02,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那傢伙真是亂來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.06,0:08:11.36,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,畢竟喝醉了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.00,0:08:14.50,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你也經常回來看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.65,0:08:20.39,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,畢竟你的工作說出去不太光彩 你可能也有些顧慮
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.88,0:08:22.91,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,但是我們畢竟是一家人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.86,0:08:25.27,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.13,0:08:28.59,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你照顧她也很辛苦吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.15,0:08:31.21,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,今後我們也會幫你一把的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.96,0:08:33.23,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,確實是很辛苦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.27,0:08:36.71,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,這之前我生氣把她趕了出去
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.77,0:08:40.89,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,被人罵我們不是以前分居 最近才把雛接來一起住嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.13,0:08:42.84,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,這是怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.97,0:08:50.51,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,壞了 壞了 醉了連個好藉口都…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.31,0:08:54.50,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,要是這樣的話 她不就是你女兒了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.63,0:08:55.74,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不 不是啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.82,0:08:58.34,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你沒瞞著什麼事情吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.75,0:09:02.42,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,新田沒說謊哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.33,0:09:08.37,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,但是… 這可是跟你的家人有關啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.37,0:09:09.85,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,等一下 老媽 別再說了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.65,0:09:13.56,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,她可是受到很大打擊 現在只記得乾燒蝦仁了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.57,0:09:15.12,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.68,0:09:17.70,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,乾燒蝦仁？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.70,0:09:24.22,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,乾燒蝦仁是 那個
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.16,0:09:27.24,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,烤得吱吱響的蝦嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.80,0:09:28.92,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.21,0:09:30.98,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,她在努力啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.52,0:09:34.91,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,看她這樣 她根本就不知道乾燒蝦仁是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.97,0:09:40.07,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,跟她剛來的時候比起來 真是長大了不少啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.42,0:09:46.00,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,她雖然還是很傻 但最近也會乖乖聽話了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.08,0:09:47.00,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然她很傻
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.73,0:09:48.97,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你說的吱吱響的是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.02,0:09:51.41,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那 那個是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.42,0:09:53.02,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,雛 夠了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.96,0:09:56.09,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,明明不知道乾燒蝦仁 辛苦你了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.16,0:09:58.10,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我很感動
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.13,0:10:00.01,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼意思
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.30,0:10:02.17,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,其實 我說謊了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.93,0:10:05.18,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,她是我的女兒
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.92,0:10:06.72,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,果然
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.74,0:10:08.60,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你為什麼要撒這種謊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.13,0:10:11.04,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我也是最近才知道她是我女兒
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.62,0:10:14.06,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我擔心跟你們說 你們也不會相信
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.93,0:10:18.10,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,但是！ 我決定不再猶豫了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.14,0:10:18.91,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,這是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.98,0:10:20.44,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,先等等 美佳
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.73,0:10:23.73,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,他這是認真的眼神
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.28,0:10:25.97,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,詳細的情況之後再說吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.51,0:10:29.08,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,總之 她是你的親女兒對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.52,0:10:31.95,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,沒錯 她是我的女兒
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.18,0:10:37.66,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,學個猥瑣大叔樣再說一遍
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.69,0:10:39.96,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,沒有戳 她舊是俺滴閨女
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.28,0:10:42.91,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,美佳
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.92,0:10:43.56,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我懂
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.54,0:10:50.51,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,首先呢 為了新田家新添的成員乾杯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.31,0:10:54.53,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,為了咱家的新成員 雛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.82,0:10:56.36,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,乾杯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.40,0:10:56.24,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}好疼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.03,0:11:00.73,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,他爸 義史帶你孫女回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.46,0:11:04.71,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,快看 你這樣的話眼神還真有點像爺爺啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.35,0:11:06.75,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼嘛這是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.76,0:11:07.38,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.54,0:11:08.81,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不 沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.39,0:11:11.59,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,義史 你也來跟你爸說兩句吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.87,0:11:19.31,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,老爸 雖然我沒能讓你見上一面
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.31,0:11:21.74,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,但你現在有孫女了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.75,0:11:22.90,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,聲太小 聲太小
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.12,0:11:25.98,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,這麼小聲可是傳達不到天國的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.25,0:11:29.38,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,今後 作為新田家一份子的雛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.39,0:11:31.24,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,就有勞老爸你多多照顧了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.67,0:11:34.33,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,義史 義史啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.43,0:11:37.65,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你會好好地愛她嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.66,0:11:38.57,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我會的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.01,0:11:40.80,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那就是說…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.43,0:11:46.17,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,今後 我也會一直好好養育她的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.91,0:11:57.31,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,來來 雛你也跟天國的爺爺說點什麼吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.58,0:11:58.34,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,Come on
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.58,0:12:01.82,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.89,0:12:07.34,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,其 其實沒什麼要說的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.93,0:12:09.96,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎
