Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.68,0:12:25.68,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\b1\bord0\fs60\fn思源黑体 CN Regular\b1\c&H000000&\3c&HFFFFFF&\pos(960,914.667)}將會對豐島區仍殘留帳篷進行清理並給予拒絕合作者處分
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.99,0:12:26.80,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,泰叔
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.22,0:12:30.52,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你知道外面的人在喊什麼嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.67,0:12:37.59,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,已經瞞不住你了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.66,0:12:41.05,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,杏子 你留心聽我說
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.55,0:12:47.91,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,這個公園 再過一陣子就不能住人了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.83,0:12:56.72,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎 終於也告訴杏子了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.12,0:12:58.75,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然時日不長
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.84,0:13:01.13,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,但是杏子搬過來後真的很快樂啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.55,0:13:04.37,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,幫她建房子的時候真的很開心
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.38,0:13:07.08,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我也從未覺得翻花繩是會讓人那麼快樂的事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.61,0:13:08.66,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.26,0:13:10.36,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,說起來啊泰叔
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.85,0:13:12.87,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,拜託詩子小姐的那件事怎麼樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.05,0:13:16.06,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,好像已經找到願意收養杏子的人家了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.11,0:13:18.84,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,這是個好機會
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.89,0:13:22.91,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,她今後的人生並不需要我們
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.07,0:13:25.85,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,希望她能過得幸福啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.20,0:13:26.89,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.00,0:13:34.73,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,做好啦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.06,0:13:36.87,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,大家
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.23,0:13:37.92,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,杏子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.67,0:13:40.14,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你差不多得開始收拾了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.76,0:13:42.53,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,這是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.34,0:13:42.46,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,230)\shad0\bord0\fn思源黑体 CN Regular\c&H645650&\pos(1310,328)}我們就在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.84,0:13:45.42,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,就像外面遊行的人一樣 我們也行動起來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.24,0:13:53.20,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,做這種事的話會被抓走的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.61,0:13:54.82,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,這已經是板上釘釘的事了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.92,0:13:56.26,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼要放棄呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.50,0:13:57.47,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,在說什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.79,0:13:58.53,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,泰叔
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.90,0:14:00.50,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,泰叔你會幫我的對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.86,0:14:02.36,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,一起來守護大家的住所吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.60,0:14:07.87,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,很遺憾…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.08,0:14:13.79,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,算了 那我自己去做點什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.39,0:14:15.95,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,他們抓不到我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.12,0:14:18.91,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,做那種事的話杏子你會被抓起來的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.95,0:14:20.04,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,絕對不行
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.12,0:14:21.96,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那 那…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.21,0:14:25.32,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,接下來會舉行最後的宴會
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.92,0:14:27.87,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,把這件事忘了好好享受吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.60,0:14:32.44,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.01,0:14:36.18,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然再過不久我們的家就會沒了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.88,0:14:38.90,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,致大家各自尋找到自己的新天地
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.88,0:14:40.57,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,乾杯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.75,0:14:41.46,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.79,0:14:47.25,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,既然我們不得不離開這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.40,0:14:49.18,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那就一起去找別的地方吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.54,0:14:50.96,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,然後大家再在那裡一起生活
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.70,0:14:53.95,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那是行不通的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.37,0:14:57.00,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,沒有其他地方能像這裡裝得下這麼多人了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.04,0:14:57.91,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,才沒那回事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.29,0:15:00.14,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,大家一起找的一定就能找到
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.45,0:15:07.03,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我 想和大家…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.04,0:15:08.35,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不要再說了！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.90,0:15:09.92,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,開口閉口都是「大家」
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.02,0:15:11.20,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,都說了沒有那種地方了！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.01,0:15:14.33,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我們僅僅是自己活下去就竭盡全力了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.55,0:15:15.90,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,別再扯上我們了！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.96,0:15:36.98,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,後藤 抱歉讓你扮黑臉了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.57,0:15:40.05,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不 才不是那麼好的事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.26,0:15:44.20,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,是他讓我覺得自己如此無能
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.38,0:15:45.83,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,一下子就那她出氣罷了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.79,0:15:48.04,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,這都是第幾次了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.49,0:15:50.47,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,後悔自己成為流浪漢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.58,0:15:52.36,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.82,0:16:15.07,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}杏子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.90,0:16:20.96,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,杏子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.29,0:16:22.13,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,算了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.20,0:16:25.49,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣會變得難以道別的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.70,0:16:35.34,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,詩子小姐 接下就…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.63,0:16:36.25,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.74,0:16:39.36,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,杏子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.20,0:16:41.19,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那再見啦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.67,0:16:42.76,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,要保重哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.22,0:17:02.17,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你個大老爺們 別哭了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.29,0:17:04.98,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,茂叔你自己不也在哭嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.99,0:17:05.79,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.14,0:17:08.05,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼嘛 泰叔你也哭了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.57,0:17:14.02,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,這孩子就是杏子嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.15,0:17:20.52,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,他們是收留你的來來軒的林夫妻
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.10,0:17:22.82,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,今天開始就來我家吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.67,0:17:26.05,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,這裝束真不得了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.79,0:17:28.66,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼就拜託您了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.80,0:17:33.00,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,來 吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.38,0:17:36.26,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.78,0:17:38.76,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不吃嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.19,0:17:42.92,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,這麼豐盛的晚餐 要花多少錢呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.50,0:17:44.84,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,在我家吃飯不用花錢哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.05,0:17:48.21,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然是匆匆忙忙做出來 不過聽你這麼說真開心
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.33,0:17:58.22,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.37,0:17:59.62,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不合你口味嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.78,0:18:01.35,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不 很好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.39,0:18:06.12,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,非常好吃 但是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.98,0:18:08.89,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.15,0:18:15.60,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,只有我一個人享用這麼好吃的飯菜真的可以嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.46,0:18:18.30,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,明明大家都各自散去
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.78,0:18:20.13,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,變成孤身一人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.96,0:18:24.09,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,只有我一個人…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.64,0:18:29.02,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,杏子 別想太多了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.48,0:18:31.19,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,還是先睡一覺休息一下比較好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.26,0:18:36.33,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,杏子她沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.57,0:18:38.36,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,這種要慢慢花時間的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.72,0:18:40.57,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,只能先等她熬過這陣子了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.59,0:18:42.25,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,但是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.01,0:18:44.59,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我覺得她是個好孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.47,0:18:48.22,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我想要儘可能地去成為她的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.20,0:18:58.01,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.95,0:19:00.75,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 對了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.42,0:19:05.14,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,已經可以不用去撿易拉罐了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.60,0:19:11.61,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我不知道我接下來該做些什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.08,0:19:14.09,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,泰叔
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.18,0:19:19.71,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,杏子 早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.89,0:19:21.93,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你們在做什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.31,0:19:24.37,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,接下來要開店幹活啦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.49,0:19:25.42,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,幹活
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.75,0:19:28.83,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我也要幹活
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.72,0:19:31.78,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你不用介意這種事的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.34,0:19:36.55,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,因為只有幹活賺錢才能吃上飯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.25,0:19:38.99,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那種事不用再做也可以…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.07,0:19:40.03,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,等等 孩子他媽
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.79,0:19:42.70,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那是誰教你的嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.00,0:19:44.81,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,是泰叔告訴我的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.87,0:19:47.33,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那你就試試看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.60,0:19:48.68,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,誒 親愛的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.99,0:19:52.12,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,杏子有好好地把泰叔的教導記在心裡呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.40,0:19:53.47,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,這不是好事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.90,0:19:55.95,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我的心裡？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.32,0:19:59.29,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊 這不是好好活在你心裡嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.08,0:20:01.28,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不只是泰叔
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.86,0:20:03.49,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,大家都教會了我很多東西
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.40,0:20:07.27,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,茂叔他教會我賣雜誌的方法
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.84,0:20:10.55,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,瞳她告訴了我有易拉罐的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.24,0:20:14.34,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,建房子的方法之類的 大家都教會了我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.39,0:20:15.32,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,其他還有…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.83,0:20:17.00,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,其他還有很多…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.35,0:20:20.79,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣啊 因為人是沒法隻身活下去的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.66,0:20:24.48,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,在杏子的心中活著很多人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.37,0:20:28.03,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我不是孤身一人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.13,0:20:30.49,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,接下來我們會教會你各種事物
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.74,0:20:32.56,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,就這樣漸漸地讓你內心充盈起來
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.22,0:20:37.69,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,而且 杏子一定也活在大家的心中
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.53,0:20:41.87,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我… 只是單純接受著大家的教導而已哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.95,0:20:43.42,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,並不止是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.44,0:20:46.79,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,和杏子至今為止一起生活的回憶
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.76,0:20:49.40,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,有好好地存在於大家心中
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.59,0:20:52.27,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.31,0:20:54.21,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.09,0:20:57.90,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 茂叔你也在啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.17,0:20:58.74,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,泰叔
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.28,0:21:04.54,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,很擔心杏子她嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.46,0:21:07.17,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,果然看得出嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.74,0:21:09.74,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,希望她忘記我們
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.02,0:21:11.48,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,乾脆地分別
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.05,0:21:14.82,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,但是我們或多或少都是犯過錯走到今天的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.94,0:21:17.56,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,就會想這次是不是也是做錯了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.96,0:21:19.96,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,但我認為
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.08,0:21:23.90,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,還有願意為我們哭泣的人在
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.51,0:21:27.09,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,再加把勁活下去看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.20,0:21:32.78,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那 那…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.02,0:21:35.11,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,大家也不是孤身一人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.15,0:21:38.25,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊 大家都不是孤身一人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.61,0:21:49.22,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.61,0:21:52.18,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,等一下 紙巾紙巾
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.20,0:21:53.44,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,也給我幾張
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.25,0:21:56.84,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,好啦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.39,0:21:59.50,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,哭成這樣可沒辦法幹活哦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.21,0:22:03.08,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
